    "Thus, for any λ ≥ 0, the Hessian matrix of the dual function has the form:∇ 2 D(λ) = 1 β E x Cov y ∼ π ⋆ (• | x;λ) [h(x, y)](11)which is a symmetric and positive semi-definite covariance matrix.",
